 <xref rid="ref34" ref-type="bibr">34</xref>
 <xref rid="ref46" ref-type="bibr">46</xref> (
 <xref ref-type="boxed-text" rid="box3">box 3</xref>). Staff also expressed frustration about the effect of precautionary measures on their ability to do their jobs.
 <xref rid="ref50" ref-type="bibr">50</xref>
